Class GetSearchHistogramResult

java.lang.Object
io.fluxzero.common.api.search.GetSearchHistogramResult
All Implemented Interfaces:
JsonType, RequestResult
public class GetSearchHistogramResult extends Object implements RequestResult
Result of a GetSearchHistogram request.

This result contains a SearchHistogram that provides time-distribution statistics over matching documents, typically for visualization purposes like timeline charts or activity heatmaps.
